data.description:
5.875% Interest rate! STOP SCROLLING! Huge opportunity to obtain an INTEREST RATE at 5.875% for the life of your loan at NO EXTRA COST TO YOU for this home ONLY!! Through List & Lock™, the seller has purchased a forward 60 days lock for the buyer at the following rate: 5.875%. Terms apply. See disclosures for more information.

Welcome to this stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home situated in the charming city of Evans. With a spacious interior spanning 2,320 square feet, this property offers a multitude of features that are sure to captivate you. As you enter, you will immediately notice the welcoming and open floor plan, creating a seamless flow throughout the home. Everything you need is located on the main floor, boasting a primary suite, additional two bedrooms, and another full bathroom, offering ample space for family and guests alike.. The lower level houses an ADDITIONAL two bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a very large and open family or game/entertainment room. The central heating and air conditioning ensure comfortable temperatures year-round, allowing you to relax in every season while having your electric bill being offset by the FULLY OWNED solar panel system. Parking is a breeze with an attached 2-car garage, providing convenient, secure storage for your vehicles. Additionally, street parking is available for guests and visitors.  Located in a vibrant community, this home offers easy access to a community park, allowing you to enjoy the outdoors and engage in recreational activities with family and friends. With its desirable location, exceptional features, and spacious interior, this 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in Evans presents an incredible opportunity. Don't miss the chance to make this house your dream home!

New Photos coming soon! No showings until Thursday 11/9!
